{"id":"1094","name":"bright-early-a-beautiful-day-in-the-neighborhood-edition","title":"Bright &amp; Early: A Beautiful Day In The Neighborhood Edition","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2008-10-10T10:11:00-05:00","tags":["barack obama","dow jones","faith hill","greer stadium","metro","MTSU","nashville sounds","stock market","terrorism","tim mcgraw"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://flickr.com/photos/gongus/2456741543/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3206/2456741543_e80839f96a.jpg?v=0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\"></a></p><p>Good morning, Nashville. After an exciting afternoon with the FBI, the TBI, the Department of Homeland Security, and various different police departments, the <a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/global/story.asp?s=9155167\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">suspected MTSU terrorist</a> is safely put away in the Rutherford County jail. Freshman Justin Davis, a dental hygiene major, lit some stuff on fire and sent an <a href=\"http://www.google.com/reader/view/?tab=my#stream/user%2F14014962846927602178%2Fstate%2Fcom.google%2Fstarred\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.google.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Email Of Mass Destruction</a> to school officials, causing them to evacuate the campus until next week. Davis is scheduled to appear in court next month for three counts of arson and one count of terrorism. Here&#x2019;s to next week being a little less eventful for the MTSU kids.</p><ul><li><strong>Gas prices dropping</strong>. Along with the stock market (down almost 700 points already this morning), <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=9152763\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">gas prices are also falling quickly</a> and are expected to hit their lowest point this year sometime in the next few weeks. Which is good news as long as there is gas at all.</li><li><strong>Tim &amp; Faith 4 Prez.</strong> What kind of morning would it be without a good presidential endorsement from a country music star? This time it&#x2019;s Tim McGraw and Faith Hill who were supposedly seen <a href=\"http://blogs.nashvillescene.com/pitw/2008/10/obama_has_faith_and_tim.php\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;blogs.nashvillescene.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">schmoozing it up</a> at Al Gore&#x2019;s Tuesday night fundraiser for Barack Obama.</li><li><strong>Bits &amp; pieces</strong>. A Clarksville teacher was <a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/17686100/detail.html#-\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">getting her drunk on</a> at school, according to students &#x2026; Tennessee is in <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20081010/NEWS0201/810100421\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">deep trouble financially</a>, may have to pull from reserves &#x2026; Metro and the Sounds are still <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20081010/NEWS0202/810100415&amp;GID=mCZ0yjoInPbEq3m2Lr/U+6J5rz3sdR8WXq2cWCM/JeU%3D\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">feuding about the lease</a> on Greer Stadium.</li></ul><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://flickr.com/photos/gongus/2456741543/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">gongus</a>.</em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/07/01/bright-early-a-beautiful-day-in-the-neighborhood-edition-2/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: A Beautiful Day In The Neighborhood Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: A Beautiful Day In The Neighborhood Edition</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/01/05/bright-early-only-in-nashville-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Only In Nashville Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Only In Nashville Edition</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}